@startuml

participant Client
participant WebServer
participant SettingsHandler
participant LittleFS

Client -> WebServer: GET /
WebServer -> Client: Send login.html
Client -> WebServer: POST / (Authenticate)
WebServer -> SettingsHandler: Get WebServer User and Password
SettingsHandler --> WebServer: User and Password
WebServer -> Client: Send Authentication prompt
Client -> WebServer: POST / (Credentials)
WebServer --> Client: Authenticate credentials
alt Successful Authentication

    Client -> WebServer: GET / (Start page)
    WebServer -> LittleFS: Retrieve start page
    LittleFS --> WebServer: Start page content
    WebServer -> Client: Send start page
else Failed Authentication
    WebServer -> Client: Send Authentication failed message
end


@enduml
